
title: main_start
---
<<declare $MY_NAME= string("a")>>
<<play_bgm "lake_happy2">>
<<play_whitenoise "bgWater_springwater1">>

<<set_character_person "Player" {$MY_NAME} "peace_1">>
<<set_character_person "Character" "B" "peace_2">>
（鲜花簇拥着我们，溪水潺潺。） #line:09f9855 
<<set_character_sprite {$MY_NAME} "peace_1">>
<<set_character_sprite "B" "peace_1">>
B:花开得真好。 #line:0b2cd4e 
（岩壁上有一大簇正盛放的小苍兰，B最喜欢那些花了。） #line:006d230 
<<set_character_shake {$MY_NAME} "up_down">>
<<set_character_sprite {$MY_NAME} "happy">>
<<set_character_sprite "B" "saying">>
B:把它们做成花环戴在你头上，唔...... #line:0d9e904 
<<set_character_sprite "B" "happy">>
<<set_character_shake "B" "left_right">>
B:（开心表情）想想那个画面，一定非常可爱吧。 #line:0120b97 
（B边说边爬上一根横垂的树枝，想去摘下岩壁上的花朵。） #line:05659c5 
<<set_character_sprite {$MY_NAME} "saying">>
{$MY_NAME}:B，注意安-- #line:0f1a741 
<<stop_bgm>>
（树枝折断了） #line:0d7301f 
<<set_character_sprite {$MY_NAME} "peace2">>
{$MY_NAME}:（惊恐表情）！！！ #line:0c4c660 
<<play_bgm lake_sadStrong>>
（她连人带花一起落下那呜咽的溪水里。） #line:0ef6cfc 
<<set_background "blackGround">>
<<clear_character_person "Player">>
<<clear_character_person "B">>

(..........) #line:07a7a58 
(..........) #line:007dd97 
<<jump room1_1>>
